        @Suspendable
public void destroy()
        Description copied from interface: SuspendableQueue
        Destroys the queue.

        Destroying the queue does not interrupt existing calls to SuspendableQueue.poll(long).

        Once the queue is destroyed, its backing datastructures in the cluster are removed.
